sequenceDiagram
  participant PDA
  participant API as Next.js API
  participant DB
  participant LOG as Audit log
  participant ROUTER as Channel router (waitUntil)
  participant RT as Realtime
  participant WEB as Patient web client
  participant MOB as Patient mobile

  PDA->>API: POST /records/upload (for patientId)
  API->>DB: insert incomingFile + fileUploadLog
  API->>LOG: writeAudit(record.uploaded)
  API-->>PDA: 200
  API->>ROUTER: waitUntil(run router)

  ROUTER->>RT: presence query — patient online?
  alt patient online
    RT-->>ROUTER: yes
    ROUTER->>RT: publish patient:{id} {recordId, byRole}
    RT-->>WEB: live event
    RT-->>MOB: live event
  else patient offline
    RT-->>ROUTER: no
    ROUTER->>MOB: Expo push (if token + pref)
    ROUTER->>API: send email (if pref)
  end

  Note over ROUTER: Best-effort — vendor failure here drops this one notification. No retry.
